    "Below, we review each training stage.",
    "Supervised Fine-tuning Stage Supervised Finetuning (SFT) maximizes the log likelihood of the ground truth response y given a user's query x:",
    "log π θ (y i |x, y <i).",
    "Efficiently optimizing the above objective is a challenging problem.",
    "We explore various strategies for SFT, which are detailed in Section 3.2."
